The age-old ghost town of Balestrino was captured in spooky wonder by a drone .
The ancient Tuscan settlement , based 40 miles south east of Genoa is shrouded in mystery with its origin and much of its history .
A number of historical earthquakes , including one in 1887 caused severe damage to the settlement 's infrastructure .
Today the town is considered to be the most famous abandoned in Italy and the area is haunted .